  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个发送通知的状态流转图，核心是描述从Education_ContentCDN到最终Education_LMS_Portal的完整流程。起点应该是ContentCDN检测到有文件需要上传的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "WAITING_FILE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以WAITING_FILE是第一个状态。那如果没有文件的情况呢？是从StudentDB直接开始吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两种入口：有文件时从ContentCDN进入WAITING_FILE，无文件时直接从StudentDB进入SENDING状态。WAITING_FILE之后也会流转到SENDING。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这两个入口和SENDING状态画好了。接下来SENDING之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SENDING之后创建SEND实体，进入REGISTERED状态。这里要分两种情况：如果有文件就走到UPLOADED，没文件直接COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING",
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：REGISTERED到COMPLETE的箭头标注是\"No file da caricare\"，REGISTERED到UPLOADED是\"File caricati\"，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "COMPLETE",
        "UPLOADED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。UPLOADED之后也是到COMPLETE。最后COMPLETE要变成ACCEPTED状态，并且ACCEPTED要指向Education_LMS_Portal作为终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE",
        "ACCEPTED",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
